Dialogs.Dialog: ...No one is watching. Now's my chance▼
We are thinking the same thing now.
You can understand without saying it, right?
It's useless after all. That's all for today.
Are you going to hug me?
I won't get into that hand.
I think I'll try to be impatient once in a while.
I'm going to be sucked in by you.
It's a ritual of reconciliation. Right?
I'm sorry I'm cold. I like you. I love you...
Emm... what time is it now?
Would you like to tell me more?
I want to stay like this.
I can't put it into words...
The feeling of a dream... I wonder.
I wish this would last forever...
Is it okay to be so sweet?
I wonder what I should do...
It's getting more and more comfortable...
If it doesn't work, stay calm.
All in the same place... not fair.
Hmm... I don't want to hear your voice.
If you don't do it, no.
It's embarrassing to stay like this...
It sounds like your heart is beating.
I've come to like it more.
It's a secret to Papa and Mama...
Fufu, you do it a lot.
Do you know what I am thinking?
I've become so bold because of you.
Hey, I want you to cover your mouth...
The end? No, I wan to kiss more.
Sorry. I can't seem to be able to stop...
I'm good, but... is it still okay?
We kissed a 100th times. Still not enough?
It's scary somehow... don't let go.
...It was too comfortable, and I was absent-minded.
Fufu, my lips are already lonely▼
I want to kiss every day.
This feelings now... let's cherish them.
Should we be lovey dovey so much?
I got a lot of energy.
Let's take care, in such times...
I'm happy just to be together...
In such time, I was nervous...
I shouldn't be happy about this, but...
Because it's sudden... I can't help it anymore...
Sometimes it's good... maybe. I'm kidding.
Don't look at my face... it's bright red.
Do you think you can't refuse?
